16:52.011 --> 16:55.179
<i> But it can heal many ailments.</i>

16:56.516 --> 16:58.582
- Do you take cash?
<i> - Mm-hmm.</i>

17:00.620 --> 17:03.120
- Here you go. $2,400.
- Hmm.

17:03.189 --> 17:05.489
- Okay! Go, go, go, go!

17:11.498 --> 17:14.732
(shanks): Hey! Hang on a sec!
I was just starting to believe!

17:14.734 --> 17:17.001
- Where is she?! Go, go!

17:21.674 --> 17:24.942
- No, you don't!
Police! You're under arrest!

17:24.978 --> 17:28.412
- You're under arrest!
- Sam! Forget that!

17:33.453 --> 17:35.753
(panting)

17:36.956 --> 17:39.157
- Hey, stop!

17:39.159 --> 17:40.758
Get back here!

17:41.694 --> 17:43.828
(tires screeching)
(screaming)

17:43.897 --> 17:46.763
(exclaiming)
zorka farkas,

17:46.800 --> 17:51.034
You... Are impressively fast,
