18:03.716 --> 18:06.050
Ammonia, phosphoric acid. Hmm.

18:06.119 --> 18:08.519
Sound like magic hungarian water
to you, wazowski?

18:08.588 --> 18:10.855
- It really does not. It sounds
like the exact composition

18:10.924 --> 18:12.923
