we can use to bring her in.

18:53.433 --> 18:56.833
- I don't know where she is.
I... I...

18:59.506 --> 19:03.174
But... Maybe I have something.

19:03.309 --> 19:05.109
My husband, vencel,

19:05.244 --> 19:07.111
