a better option.

19:42.916 --> 19:46.751
- Gentlemen, meet lucky spacek,

19:46.886 --> 19:49.553
Our new potential supplier.

19:52.625 --> 19:55.492
He lives within five kilometres
of four dealers

19:55.528 --> 19:57.361
