for pink-cocaine sales,

19:57.430 --> 20:01.298
And he's got an association with
coyote member bingo ramirez,

20:01.434 --> 20:05.570
Whom I believe you connected...
To will french.

20:05.705 --> 20:10.074
We should get a team
over to his place asap,
start surveilling him.

20:10.076 --> 20:13.144
