because he lives near someone
who committed a crime?

20:13.279 --> 20:16.180
- Context, greene.
Plus, the numbers don't lie.

20:16.182 --> 20:18.182
We should name this thing,
this algorithm.

20:18.184 --> 20:20.584
Something spiffy.
How about crack whacker?

20:22.055 --> 20:24.154
Okay, dope dotter?

20:24.190 --> 20:26.057
