22:13.499 --> 22:15.699
- You kidding me?
I wouldn't miss this
for the world.

22:17.169 --> 22:19.503
I know it sounds cliché,
but you actually are glowing
right now.

22:19.505 --> 22:22.907
- You certainly are.
