22:41.527 --> 22:43.928
- I don't know. He's a nice guy.

22:45.798 --> 22:48.065
(sighing)
alright, look.

22:48.134 --> 22:50.401
Sam and I are in a bit
of a bind,

22:50.403 --> 22:53.471
And we need the fbi to pressure
bitcrypt to share some
of their decryption software.

22:53.606 --> 22:55.873
We don't have time to deal
with the rcmp.

22:55.875 --> 22:58.609
It's a huge, huge part
of our case.

22:58.678 --> 23:00.945
Karina,
I would really appreciate it.

23:00.947 --> 23:03.747
