and maybe participated
in our shower.

23:07.653 --> 23:09.620
- Okay, well,
when's the gender reveal?

23:09.689 --> 23:11.288
- It's in five hours.

23:11.290 --> 23:13.124
(awkward laughter)

23:13.259 --> 23:14.891
- Ah...
