25:04.504 --> 25:06.870
- Mm. Mm...

25:08.340 --> 25:11.008
- Elijah's sending over
the software tomorrow morning.

25:12.245 --> 25:15.145
- Really? That was fast.
- Kelly, I...

25:16.349 --> 25:18.315
