27:11.530 --> 27:13.363
I-I realize now, I just...

27:14.533 --> 27:16.366
St-steve, I really...

27:18.170 --> 27:20.404
I really need closure.

27:20.473 --> 27:22.272
- That's great.

27:23.676 --> 27:27.410
I'm not gonna make any excuses.
I wish I could go back and--

27:27.446 --> 27:29.646
